extends email-layout

block content
  h2 #{msg.center_name}
  p Dear #{msg.lead_name},
  p Thank you for contacting our team at #{msg.center_name}.
  p Across the world and in #{msg.center_area}, we create magical learning spaces where children flourish and thrive.
  p.title-email What we offer
  ul
    li International preschool and daycare for 8 months to 6 years.
    li Learning spaces infused with cutting edgy pedagogy.
    li Customized education for each child.
    li Half-day and full-day childcare services.
    li STEM-based learning.
    li Explorer and Skill days.
    li Afterschool programs.
  p.title-email Kido Club
  p
    | Free access to
    a(href=msg.activities target="_blank")  Kido Club
    |  - An exclusive portal for Kido parents for Events, activities, courses, and more.
  br
  h3 BOOK A SCHOOL TOUR
  p My name is #{msg.spoc}, and I invite interested parents to visit the center to see our fantastic settings, meet our teachers and learn all about us! You can reach out to me at #{msg.email} or by calling #{(msg.whatsapp && msg.contact) ? `${msg.whatsapp} (WhatsApp Number) / ${msg.contact} (Contact Number)` : msg.whatsapp ? `${msg.whatsapp} (WhatsApp Number)` : msg.contact ? `${msg.contact} (Contact Number)` : ""}.
  p Watch the video to know more about us -&nbsp;
    a(href=`${msg.video}` target="_blank") Click here.
  p.title-email There's a lot more
  p
    | Parents can visit our
    a(href=msg.website target="_blank")  Website
    |  to learn more about
    a(href="https://www.kidoschools.com/in/in-curriculum/" target="_blank")  our curriculum
    |  and our
    a(href="https://www.kidoschools.com/in/in-events/" target="_blank")  latest events. (They are free!)
  p We look forward to seeing you at Kido.
  p
    | Best Regards,
    br
    | #{msg.sal} #{msg.spoc}
    br
    | #{msg.designation}, #{msg.center_name}
  //- p.grey-mark This mail is auto-generated mail. Please do not reply to this mail.